SME Client Portal — LICENCE TBD
===============================

The final licence has not been chosen yet. Planned options (to be
decided before the first public release):

1. **AGPL-3.0** on the whole codebase.
   Protects against a competitor running the hosted service from a
   private fork without contributing back. Matches the Plausible,
   Cal.com, and Chatwoot model.

2. **Open-core**: MIT on the `app/` core plus a commercial licence on
   `app/platform/` (the SaaS layer with Identity, tenant CRUD, billing,
   etc.). Matches the Sentry / Supabase model. Core can be forked and
   run single-tenant for free; running a hosted multi-tenant SaaS
   requires the commercial addon.

Until the licence is final, the code in this repository is copyrighted
by 4MEX s.r.o. All rights reserved. Contributions are welcome under
the understanding that the final licence will be one of the two
listed above.

For questions contact: opensource@4mex.cz
